    <item>
      <title>中国投资者将数十亿美元资金转移到香港银行，寻求更高的收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/chinese-move-billions-into-hong-kong-banks-seeking-higher-yields</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股有限公司第一季度在香港吸引了超过 13 万名新银行客户。中国银行（香港）在 2023 年新增了 20 万名跨境客户，而恒生银行去年为非居民开设的新账户数量增长了 342%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/chinese-move-billions-into-hong-kong-banks-seeking-higher-yields</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲债券跟随美国涨势；关注印度开盘：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国劳动力市场降温的迹象增强了美联储降息的预期，债券市场在亚洲早盘跟随美国国债走高。股市则在寻找方向。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 22:31:58 GMT</pubDate>
